The '''{{PAGENAME}}''' is an abandoned building that was once used by [[The Cirque du Freak]] to show the freak show. Years after the freak show had left, [[Steve]] converted it into a trap for [[Darren]] and other [[Vampaneze Lord hunters]] to fall in to. It is here where Steve killed [[Shancus]]. 

