'''Cal Grady''' was [[Grubbs]]' (and [[Bill-E Spleen|Billy]]'s) father and [[Dervish]]'s brother. It appeared that he was happily married to [[Sharon Grady|Sharon]], his wife, but it turned out that while visiting Dervish in [[Carcery Vale]] he had a one night stand with a local woman, resulting in the birth of Bill-E. 

{{DEFAULTSORT:Grady, Cal}} 

[[Category:Demonata Characters]]

'''Ma''' and Pa Spleen are [[Bill-E]]'s over protective grandparents. In ''[[Blood Beast]]'', they are killed by [[Grubbs]] when he is struck with [[lycanthropy]], but later revealed to have been killed by [[Juni Swan]] (or Nadia Moore).

{{DEFAULTSORT:Spleen, Ma}}

